page.title: 18TRAFFIC
page.content:
There is more traffic in Withernwick than you expect. When we did a survey of traffic coming from Aldbrough and passing through school and traffic coming through Withernwick starting at 8:30 am and ending at 3:30 pm this was the result.
Going to Aldbrough {Motor {Cars Tractors Lorries Buses bikes Vans 92 6 11 1 0 26
Going the other way <into Withernwick>. {Motor {Cars Tractors Lorries Buses bikes Vans 77 3 19 1 2 20
The number of vehicles passing in 7 hours was 259. There was only 1 bicycle. {
